'''Aduzewiɣ''' (s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tanglizt]]: Infrared) iga yat taẓḍaṛt taẓaṛumɣnaḍisant tffuɣ zzɣ uwelaf ittiweẓeṛan dar ufgan, tiɣezi n teyyuɣt n ifutunn gis teɣezzif s imikk f xettalli illan dar tifawet taẓggʷaɣet.
Ur neẓḍar att nẓeṛ s tiṭṭ macc neẓḍar as-tt nessyafa g tewllafet n tireɣi.

* Ar ittefuyyuɣ uduzewiɣ g ku tifgga illan g wakal s unuɣ n tireɣi, s iskʷfal iwer imsasan, macc tafuket d takat ad igan iɣbula nns i bahra igguten. Iga uduzewiɣ yat zzɣ tiɣarasin is a ttemattay tireɣi zzɣ tasga s tayyaḍ.
* Zzɣ isseqdac n uduzewiɣ: inzaḍen - ingmamen n wannay g yiḍ - ismaqqalen - ilafen isredasen - tiɣeri n imahellawen - tiɣeri n idrizen - tusrimin tiqqburin - ingmamen n ussreɣ - itilifunn ...
